 {\"sentence\": \"33  5  Link copied!\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 971, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Share  Link copied!\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 992, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Share  Letsile Tebogowrote his name in his country's history book when he earnedBotswana's firstOlympic gold medal-and his people were eager to celebrate it with him.\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1160, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The sprinter beat Team USA stars Noah Lyles and Kenny Bednarek in the men's 200-meter final on August 8.\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1268, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1182, \"end\": 1190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.892261202406546, \"rank\": 0.12047040716231834, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1197, \"end\": 1207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 1212, \"end\": 1226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kenny Bednarek\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He won in 19.46 seconds, the fourth-fastest time ever.\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1323, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Additionally, he led his team to a silver medal in the 4x400m relay.\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Image credits:tebogo_letsile_  Botswana President Mokgweetsi Masisi declared a public holiday in honor of his achievement.\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1517, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1426, \"end\": 1434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.450276949297196e-14, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}, {\"begin\": 1445, \"end\": 1462, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mokgweetsi_Masisi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mokgweetsi Masisi\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mokgweetsi_Masisi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mokgweetsi_Masisi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Tuesday (August 13), he declared a half-holiday, this time to celebrate Team Botswana's triumphant homecoming.\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1631, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1598, \"end\": 1606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.450276949297196e-14, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hundreds of fans gathered at the Sir Seretse Khama International Airport to welcome theOlympic heroand the other athletes on the team as they touched down at the capital, Gaborone.\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1813, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1666, \"end\": 1705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sir_Seretse_Khama_International_Airport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sir Seretse Khama International Airport\", \"types\": [\"Q1248784\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sir_Seretse_Khama_International_Airport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sir_Seretse_Khama_International_Airport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Image credits:tebogo_letsile_  Traditional dancers wearing animal skins and beads were there to start the party as the athletes appeared, theBBCreported.\", \"from\": 1817, \"to\": 1970, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"President Mokgweetsi Masisi was present to greet the athletes and even showed off some of his moves on the tarmac.\", \"from\": 1972, \"to\": 2086, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1982, \"end\": 1999, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mokgweetsi_Masisi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mokgweetsi Masisi\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mokgweetsi_Masisi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mokgweetsi_Masisi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Later,over30,000 fansfilled Botswana National Stadiumto see the 21-year-old's medal in person and celebrate his historic victory for the country.\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2233, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2116, \"end\": 2124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.450276949297196e-14, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by ESPN (@espn)        A post shared by TAG Heuer (@tagheuer)    In addition to his medal, there are other prizes in store for the sprinter.\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2395, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2258, \"end\": 2262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.264037981984671e-14, \"text\": \"ESPN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According toTMZ, the government will award him a four-bedroom home, as well as some cash.\", \"from\": 2396, \"to\": 2485, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The young athletededicated his achievementto his late mother, who passed away in May 2024 after a brief illness.\", \"from\": 2487, \"to\": 2599, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He also competed in bright orange Nikes with a sticker with her date of birth, 23.12.1980.\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2690, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's basically me carrying her through every stride that I take inside the field,\\\" Letsile said afterwinning gold.\", \"from\": 2692, \"to\": 2807, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To take her [with me], it gives me a lot of motivation.\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2865, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She's watching up there, and she's really, really happy.\\\"\", \"from\": 2866, \"to\": 2923, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Anyone can write on Bored Panda.Start writing!\", \"from\": 2939, \"to\": 2985, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Bored Panda onGoogle News!\", \"from\": 2987, \"to\": 3020, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2994, \"end\": 3005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bored_Panda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bored Panda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bored_Panda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bored_Panda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow us onFlipboard.com/@boredpanda!\", \"from\": 3022, \"to\": 3060, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"33  5  33  5  Link copied!\", \"from\": 3064, \"to\": 3090, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Share  Link copied!\", \"from\": 3092, \"to\": 3111, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Share  Writer,Entertainment News Writer  With a degree in social science and a love for culture, I approach entertainment journalism at Bored Panda with a research-driven mindset.\", \"from\": 3113, \"to\": 3292, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3249, \"end\": 3260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bored_Panda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bored Panda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bored_Panda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bored_Panda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I write about celebrity news, Hollywood highlights, and viral stories that spark curiosity worldwide.\", \"from\": 3293, \"to\": 3